[
  {
    "text": "日常生活的织锦",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.10071910091700689,
      "left": 0.3627450829248366,
      "width": 0.27450980620914983,
      "height": 0.030303029040404043
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "早晨的阳光照亮了安静的街道,温暖的光线穿过树叶,在地面上投下斑驳的影子。鸟儿在",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.16446939418877496,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.7647058887254882,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "树上轻声歌唱,它们的歌声欢快而清",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.1871966659690781,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.313725492810457,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "脆,唤醒了沉睡的城市,开始新的一天充满",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.1871966659690781,
      "left": 0.43137254673202563,
      "width": 0.37254902271241724,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "希望和可",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.1871966659690781,
      "left": 0.8039215694444428,
      "width": 0.07843137320261406,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "能性。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2099239377493811,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.058823529901960686,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "科技的发展正在以前所未有的速度改变我们的生活方式和工作模式。每天都有新的创新和",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2449618150773482,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.7647058887254882,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "发明出现,从人工智能到可再生能源,这些技术进步深",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2676890868576512,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.4705882392156855,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "刻地影响着社会的方方面面,重塑",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2676890868576512,
      "left": 0.5882352931372542,
      "width": 0.2941176495098026,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "着我们与世界互动",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.29041635863795434,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.15686274640522851,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "的方式。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.29041635863795434,
      "left": 0.2745098003267971,
      "width": 0.07843137320261424,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "古代文明建造了令人惊叹的纪念碑和建筑奇迹,这些宏伟的结构历经千年依然屹立不倒。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.32640120562343405,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.7647058887254882,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "从埃及的金字塔到中国的长城,这些建筑不仅展示了我们祖先的非凡智慧和惊人的创造",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.34912847740373704,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.7450980454248346,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "力,也见证了人类文明的辉煌历程。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3718557491840401,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.313725492810457,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "教育是",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4068936265120072,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.058823529901960686,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "推",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4068936265120072,
      "left": 0.17647058382352931,
      "width": 0.01960784330065356,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "动社会进步和个人发展的根本基础。通过系统",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4068936265120072,
      "left": 0.19607842712418289,
      "width": 0.39215686601307126,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "够获得改",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4296208982923102,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.07843137320261427,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "善",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4296208982923102,
      "left": 0.19607842712418289,
      "width": 0.01960784330065354,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "自己生活和周围社区所需",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4296208982923102,
      "left": 0.21568627042483643,
      "width": 0.2156862763071892,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "的各种工具、技能和深",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4296208982923102,
      "left": 0.43137254673202563,
      "width": 0.19607843300653557,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "未来做出贡献。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4523481700726133,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.1372549031045749,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "的学习和持续的知识积累,人们能",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4068936265120072,
      "left": 0.5882352931372542,
      "width": 0.2941176495098024,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "刻见解,从而为建设更美好",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4296208982923102,
      "left": 0.6274509797385613,
      "width": 0.235294119607842,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "的",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4296208982923102,
      "left": 0.8627450993464033,
      "width": 0.01960784330065354,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "大自然慷慨地提供了无与伦比的美丽景观和维持生命所必",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4873860474005805,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.490196082516339,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "需",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4873860474005805,
      "left": 0.6078431364379078,
      "width": 0.01960784330065354,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "气到纯净的水源,从肥沃的土壤到多样",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5101133191808834,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.33333333611111055,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "的生物。保",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5101133191808834,
      "left": 0.45098039003267926,
      "width": 0.09803921650326779,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "护",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5101133191808834,
      "left": 0.5490196065359471,
      "width": 0.01960784330065354,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "和珍惜环",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5101133191808834,
      "left": 0.5686274498366006,
      "width": 0.07843137320261416,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "任,更是确",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5328405909611865,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.09803921650326781,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "保后代子孙能够继续享受地球奇观的关键。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5328405909611865,
      "left": 0.21568627042483643,
      "width": 0.3725490227124177,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "的各种宝贵资源。从清新的空",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4873860474005805,
      "left": 0.6274509797385613,
      "width": 0.25490196290849537,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "境",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5101133191808834,
      "left": 0.6470588230392148,
      "width": 0.01960784330065354,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "不仅是我们这一代人的责",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5101133191808834,
      "left": 0.6666666663398683,
      "width": 0.21568627630718856,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "有效的交流在不同文化、民族和国家之间架",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5688254379466663,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.37254902271241763,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "起了理解与合作的重要桥梁。语言作为人类最",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5688254379466663,
      "left": 0.49019607663398634,
      "width": 0.3921568660130703,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "伟大的发明之一,使我们能够跨越地理和文化的界限,分享彼",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5915527097269694,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.5294117691176461,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "此的想法、经验和智慧,从",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5915527097269694,
      "left": 0.6470588230392148,
      "width": 0.235294119607842,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "而建立起相互理解、尊重和信任的关系。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6142799815072724,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.35294117941176406,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "科学研究通过严谨的方法和不懈的探索,正在逐步揭示宇宙中",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6493178588352395,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.5294117691176461,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "那些深藏的奥秘和规律。每",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6493178588352395,
      "left": 0.6470588230392148,
      "width": 0.235294119607842,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "一个新的发现都像是打开了一扇通往未知世界的大门,同时也带来了更多令人着迷的问",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6720451306155426,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.7450980454248346,
      "height": 0.015151514520201985
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "题,激励着科学家们继续前行,探索更广阔的未知领域。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6947724023958456,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.490196082516339,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "艺术以其独特的方式表达和传递那些超越语言文字限制的深",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7298102797238128,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.5098039258169925,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "刻情感和抽象思想。无论是绘",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7298102797238128,
      "left": 0.6274509797385613,
      "width": 0.25490196290849537,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "画、音乐、雕塑还是文学,这些富有创意的艺术作品不仅能够激发人们的想象力和创造",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7525375515041159,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.7450980454248346,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "力,还能挑战我们既有的观念,引导我们从全新的角度来审视和理解",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7752648232844189,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.5882352990196067,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "这个复杂多彩的世",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7752648232844189,
      "left": 0.7058823529411753,
      "width": 0.15686274640522804,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
